      interface.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[ITextureSamplerCube::unique_ptr CreateTextureSamplerCube();]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="ITextureSamplerCube!cobalt.graphics.ITextureSamplerCube">
        A freshly constructed <TypeRef>ITextureSamplerCube</TypeRef> object, wrapped in a <TypeRef>unique_ptr</TypeRef>.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
